metadata.name: Invincible Beauty
metadata.description:
You all know that the real, horrific and terrifying war is going on in Ukraine now.

Attacking Ukraine, Russia is trying to destroy freedom by slavery, truth by lies, courage by cowardice, beauty and culture by hopeless darkness and degradation. This is the war between good and evil, beauty and ugliness. 

And as you know, beauty will save the world, and good will always triumph over evil. We believe in the best, glory to Ukraine!

CINEMA 4D | REDSHIFT | 2160X2160 I JPEG
